name: Planning
content: The team should make an outline of the work-division over the duration of the project

name: Initial user studies
content: Identifying requirements from the digital libraries' audience

name: Policy-making
content: Rules and standards to be followed for the project

name: Collection development
content: Process of gathering contents of the digital library

name: Architecture design and implementation
content: Constructing a framework to support the streamlined development and implementation

name: User interface design and implementation
content: Design and code the interface between the library and the user

name: Metadata
content: Gather and maintain metadata information about the collection

name: Service implementation
content: Include access-based services for increased benefit

name: Preservation
content: Follow-up process of maintaining collection up-to-date
